template: SELECT MIN(name.id) AS name_id, MIN(person_info.person_id) AS person_info_person_id FROM title, cast_info, movie_link, person_info, name, role_type WHERE cast_info.person_id = name.id AND cast_info.movie_id = title.id AND cast_info.role_id = role_type.id AND person_info.person_id = name.id AND movie_link.movie_id = title.id AND person_info.note = %s AND name.name NOT LIKE %s AND title.production_year BETWEEN 1955 AND 2000;
